  ],
  "remarks": "JSC “Research and Production Corporation ‘Precision Instrumentation Systems’”, also known as JSC “NPK ‘SPP’”, is one of the main military-industrial companies in Russia. In particular, it produces aircraft systems such as SEER, MOS, OES-52, OLS-container and OLS. These aircraft systems are being used in Russian military aircraft such as SU-27 and attack helicopter KA-52, used by the Russian Armed Forces in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
